Clarke Leads Johnson by Two Shots, Mickelson by Three at British Open

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-07-17T15:55:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/clarke-leads-johnson-by-two-shots-mickelson-by-three-at-british-open.html
Darren Clarke leads  Dustin Johnson 
by two shots in the final round of golf’s  British Open .  Clarke is 2-under par through 12 holes today at Royal St.
George’s in Sandwich,  England , and 7-under for the tournament.  Johnson, playing in the final group with Clarke, is 1-under
for his round and 5-under overall.  Phil Mickelson  was at 6-under
after 10 holes, but bogeyed the 11th and 13th holes to drop
three shots back.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  